Well As far as the hoppers in dawnshroud goes they are the easiest place to get superb and flawless hopper hides but hardly the only place. While I find it highly inconvient for me when the Sambata's are up I do not begrudge Twig his trying to do a quest that requires the tribals up. I have been there on the days when he has been pulling  half the cave at a time and while it can be a bit annoying at times, as going in deep for 1 or 2 hoppers can lead to some very ugly hopper trains he can handle those that he pulls so no complaints from me. when the hoppers in dawnshroud are not up I go to mons letalis or scarlet desert to get hides to skill up on simple as that. Not as convient mind you but not a skill ending disaster either. And you won't see me ever buying a hopper hide for 100+ plat esp not when the finished product is selling for peanuts. I farm my own or get it from guildies. So go for it Twig just please remember to reset the hoppers back after your done with your quest.<br>
